{"id":"5e9c33649b6559241525e057","title":"Single of The Week: Best Coast- When I’m With You","content":"<p><a rel=\"attachment wp-att-2290\" href=\"https://admin.</p><p>crackintheroad.com/music/2069-single-of-the-week-best-coast-when-i%e2%80%99m-with-you/attachment/bestcoast_press-1\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-totallysizedforever wp-image-2290\" title=\"bestcoast_press-1\" src=\"https://api.crackintheroad.com/uploads/2010/08/bestcoast_press-1-740x404.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"740\" height=\"404\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Best Coast’s</strong> debut album <em>‘Crazy For You’</em> is a beauty. 13 songs of pure sun kissed fuzz;  it’s heart achingly honest and toe-tappingly lovely, as all surf-pop should be. The record is managing to achieve critical and commercial success, gaining fans such as <strong>Thurston Moore</strong> and <strong>Bill Murray</strong>; not bad for a first LP.</p>\n<p><em>‘When I’m With You’</em> is the highlight for many. Full of beautiful harmonies and low-fidelity fuzz, it captures perfectly the painful innocence of the album. So here it is for you to enjoy/re-enjoy, depending on your persuasion.</p>\n<p><object classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\" width=\"640\" height=\"385\" codebase=\"https://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\"><param name=\"allowFullScreen\" value=\"true\" /><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" /><param name=\"src\" value=\"https://www.youtube.com/v/8Sj5_WITMpA&hl=en_US&fs=1\" /><param name=\"allowfullscreen\" value=\"true\" /><embed type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"640\" height=\"385\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/v/8Sj5_WITMpA&hl=en_US&fs=1\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></embed></object></p>\n","slug":"2069-single-of-the-week-best-coast-when-im-with-you","category":"music","date":1280868311000,"wpid":2069,"isSticky":false,"featured_image":{"width":150,"height":150,"src":"2010/08/bestcoast_press-1-150x150.jpg","placeholder":"data:image/jpeg;base64, "},"createdAt":1587295076263,"updatedAt":1588443779948,"author":"5e9b68b27a1236eccfeb1d24","old_image":"2010/08/bestcoast_press-1-150x150.jpg","categories":["music"]}